{
  "stem": "676.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Or we would be forever counted.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They always counted us, you know?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we'd lay in the barracks.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we just did nothing, you know, those couple of weeks, you know?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Just waited till we get food again.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Once a day, we got the food.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Once a day, we got the bread and the black coffee.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No hot food.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was supposed to be, yeah.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember my cousin, when he came to Auschwitz and he didn't know what was going on.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were giving out that coffee.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he says, no, I want from the other one.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I want the tea.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that woman took and she slapped him on the face.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She slapped him.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She says, what do you think you are?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You can't ask tea.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[LAUGHTER] After that, he knew that he can't ask for anything.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So you were-- you were in these camps.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And like you said, you were just sort of waiting.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Until they sent-- ship us again.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't know where to.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Maybe I was too young.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Maybe others did know maybe something, but not much.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I certainly didn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the barracks, there was Jewish administration.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had-- they called them the kapos.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
